<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Foreach on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/foreach/</link><description>Recent content in Foreach on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/foreach/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] MyBatis Dynamic SQL Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/mybatis-dynamic-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/mybatis-dynamic-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="mybatis-dynamic-sql-error-fix"&gt;MyBatis Dynamic SQL Error Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A MyBatis dynamic SQL error occurs when XML-based dynamic SQL tags are malformed, reference non-existent parameters, or have incorrect collection bindings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common messages:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;ExecutorException: Dynamic SQL error: &amp;lt;foreach&amp;gt; property not found&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;BindingException: Parameter 'list' not found. Available parameters are [collection, list]&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;SQLSyntaxErrorException: ... near 'AND'&lt;/code&gt; (empty dynamic SQL generates bad SQL)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MyBatis processes &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;if&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;foreach&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;choose&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;where&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, and &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;set&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; tags at runtime. Errors occur when the XML is malformed or parameter names do not match the mapper method signature.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>PHP Warning: Invalid argument supplied for foreach()</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/php/warning-in-foreach/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/php/warning-in-foreach/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="php-warning-invalid-argument-supplied-for-foreach"&gt;PHP Warning: Invalid argument supplied for foreach()&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This warning occurs when you use &lt;code&gt;foreach&lt;/code&gt; on a variable that is not an array or an object that implements &lt;code&gt;Traversable&lt;/code&gt;. PHP cannot iterate over scalar values, &lt;code&gt;null&lt;/code&gt;, or non-iterable types.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using &lt;code&gt;foreach&lt;/code&gt; on a variable that is &lt;code&gt;null&lt;/code&gt; or not an array&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A function returning a non-array value when an array was expected&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Database query returning &lt;code&gt;false&lt;/code&gt; instead of an array&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="validate-before-iterating"&gt;Validate Before Iterating&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;foreach&lt;/span&gt; ($data &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; $item) { &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;...&lt;/span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;is_array&lt;/span&gt;($data)) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;foreach&lt;/span&gt; ($data &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; $item) { &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;...&lt;/span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-the-null-coalescing-operator"&gt;Use the Null Coalescing Operator&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;foreach&lt;/span&gt; ($data &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;??&lt;/span&gt; [] &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; $item) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; $item;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-function-return-values"&gt;Check Function Return Values&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;mysqli_query&lt;/span&gt;($conn, $query);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; ($result) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; ($row &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;mysqli_fetch_assoc&lt;/span&gt;($result)) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; $row[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;name&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;];
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// This triggers the warning
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$data &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;foreach&lt;/span&gt; ($data &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; $item) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; $item;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Warning: Invalid argument supplied for foreach()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$data &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;];
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;foreach&lt;/span&gt; ($data &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; $item) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; $item &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/php/warning-count/"&gt;PHP Warning: count()&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/php/warning-in-in-array/"&gt;PHP Warning: in_array()&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/php/notice-undefined-variable/"&gt;PHP Notice: Undefined Variable&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] PHP each() Deprecated — Replace with foreach() Migration</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/deprecated/php/each-to-foreach/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/deprecated/php/each-to-foreach/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="solution-php-each-deprecated--replace-with-foreach-migration"&gt;[Solution] PHP each() Deprecated — Replace with foreach() Migration&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;each()&lt;/code&gt; function was deprecated in PHP 7.2 and removed in PHP 8.0. It was commonly used in older PHP code to iterate over arrays by returning the current key-value pair and advancing the internal pointer. Modern PHP code should use &lt;code&gt;foreach&lt;/code&gt; loops, which are cleaner, faster, and more readable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-youll-see"&gt;What You&amp;rsquo;ll See&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On PHP 7.2 through 7.4:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Deprecated: each() is deprecated in /path/to/script.php on line X
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;On PHP 8.0+:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>